-- Blackstone head of Asia Chae to relocate to New York from H.K. - memo
-- By Stephen Aldred
-- Thu Apr 03, 2014 10:52PM EDT
-- None



HONG KONG, April 4 (Reuters) - Blackstone Group's <BX.N> head of private equity for Asia, senior managing director Michael Chae, is returning to New York after three years in Hong Kong, according to an internal memo seen by Reuters.

Chae will continue to oversee Blackstone's operations in Asia but will take back responsibility for media communications investments, the memo said.